( AFP ) Related Story : Scores dead after strong quake hits China Map : China The search is continuing for survivors of a powerful earthquake in China ' s south - west that has killed nearly 180 people and injured around 7 , 000 . The shallow earthquake struck Sichuan province just after 8 : 00am yesterday ( local time ), prompting a major rescue operation in the same area where 87 , 000 people were reported dead or missing in a massive quake in 2008 . Local seismologists registered the quake at magnitude 7 . 0 , while the US Geological Survey recorded it as 6 . 6 .